Version:0.3

OASISFormat: 0.4 
Name: Electrum Analyzer
Synopsis: Formal analysis for the Electrum formal specification language
Authors:
  David Chemouil,
  Julien Brunel,
  Denis Kuperberg
Maintainers: david.chemouil+electrum@onera.fr
Copyrights: 
  (c) 2014-2015 Onera
